SysML:Requirement.Text: Climate control unit in max mode shall not be louder than engine.
Mass of the unit shall not exceed 2 percent of the total car mass.

SysML:functionalRequirement.Text: It must be possible to set and maintain desired temperature in the cabin.
Unit shall be able to heat and cool.
